Ranger Help for: mine
=====================

SYNTAX:      mine
             mine stone
USAGE:       Underground, hills, or mountains
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     25
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to gather useful stone from rough terrain.
The Ranger must have a field kit prepared with 'make tools'. Mining
stores fieldstone and flint in the Ranger's wildcraft pouch instead
of creating loose rocks in inventory.

Fieldstone and flint are used by survival crafts such as make tools
and mix weapon paste. Mining depletes a room for a while, so Rangers
need to move through the wild instead of stripping one place forever.
